This is baby Idah!!

“With each day that passes I know your love for me! In the moments when I stand strong, in the seasons when I’m weak. I call Your name, and You are there”

Me and God … we go together REAL BAD!!! 

Things that were meant to destroy me end up being the ladder that I needed to elevate!!

I’m not “lucky” I am GOD’s

Water wave glueless wig. Mine is 16” and 180 density!!!
No combs so it sits well on my locs but comes with a secure adjustable band in the back! 
Aah we hit the jackpot with this one ladies!
It DOES NOT shed!!! I’m so shook!

So I dropped my mousse, bottle broke and it spilled 🤣 hence the S-curl but typically just water and mousse will hold your curls better! Make the curls pop!!!
